articles.title: Tensions high on NATO’s border with Belarus after Wagner troops move closer - CNN
articles.description: Poland will deploy more troops at the border with Belarus after it accused Minsk of violating its airspace, raising tensions between the NATO member and a key Kremlin ally in an increasingly volatile security landscape in Europe.
